title: Microsoft Ignite Australia
eventShortDescription: ​Microsoft Ignite Australia happens to attract some of the world’s brightest minds. It’s your chance to meet them, extend your professional network and deepen personal connections. Thoughts will be sparked. Questions will be answered. Fun will be had.​
